{"tid":2257314,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Denis Villeneuve, Jake Gyllenhaal, Nolan細佬合作新劇“The Son”","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T18:38:50.000Z","uid":157092,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7064b5c4dab27a47ff6cf50dcfccbb31fcc8b6a2","tid":2257314,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aVkgNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aVkgNC.jpg&h=6a0ab575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://collider.com/jake-gyllenhaal-hbo-show-the-son-denis-villeneuve-director/?utm_medium=twitter&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;amp&amp;utm_campaign=collidersocial&amp;utm_medium=twitter&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcollider.com%2Fjake-gyllenhaal-hbo-show-the-son-denis-villeneuve-director%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dtwitter%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26amp%26utm_campaign%3Dcollidersocial%26utm_medium%3Dtwitter%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72Pf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2fd85903\" target=\"_blank\">https://collider.com/jake-gyllenhaal-hbo-show-the-son-denis-villeneuve-director/?utm_medium=twitter&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;amp&amp;utm_campaign=collidersocial&amp;utm_medium=twitter&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\nJake Gyllenhaal&nbsp;has set up a new television project that will no doubt attract major attention. The project in question is a limited series adaptation of&nbsp;Jo Nesb&oslash;&lsquo;s book&nbsp;The Son. If Nesb&oslash;&rsquo;s name rings a bell, it&rsquo;s because also wrote&nbsp;The Snowman, which was (infamously) adapted into a 2017 movie starring&nbsp;Michael Fassbender. <br />\n<br />\nGyllenhaal will both star in and executive produce through his Nine Stories banner. the limited series adaptation of&nbsp;The Son&nbsp;over at HBO. As previously mentioned, this is Gyllenhaal&rsquo;s second big TV project but it&rsquo;s also his second TV project&nbsp;at HBO. Back in April 2019, it was announced Gyllenhaal would also star in the&nbsp;limited series&nbsp;Lake Success, which seems to still be in the early production stages. <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>Gyllenhaal will also reunite with his&nbsp;Enemy&nbsp;and&nbsp;Prisoners&nbsp;director&nbsp;Denis Villeneuve&nbsp;for&nbsp;The Son. Villeneuve is set to direct all episodes of the limited series as well as executive produce.</strong></span></span> And, as if this project didn&rsquo;t already pack a punch with this creative duo leading the way, HBO notes in their announcement that&nbsp;<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>Westworld&nbsp;duo&nbsp;Jonathan Nolan&nbsp;and&nbsp;Lisa Joy&nbsp;have also boarded&nbsp;The Son&nbsp;as executive producers</strong></span></span> under their Kilter Films banner."},{"pid":"2063bbd01e20e8509b98b69aac4ad7abd889c501","tid":2257314,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正"},{"pid":"525e08a46cbad07aaee9efc5cbd5954869439986","tid":2257314,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e3775af4663ba7339f920dbb260b025bec6541","tid":2257314,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都負評"},{"pid":"3b5604c7991253ad88ac4843e3e7de422c2ae37a","tid":225731